We completed Ceacht 12.1 on page 56 in pairs.
  *
We then completed the revision questions, Ceacht 12.2 & 12.3 on page 57/58 =
orally in pairs.
  *
We also learnt a new word 'P=F3ig=EDn=ED Gr=E9ine' which is the word for fr=
eckles but literally translates to 'little kisses from the sun'!
  *
We will be moving onto Caibidil 14 lch 62 an tseachtain seo chugainn!

